ocity. Finally, we propose that $\\rm{HCN}$ and\n$\\rm{HCNH^+}$, being chemically co-evolving, could be used in future\nobservational studies aiming to measure the ion-neutral drift velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 18:10:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
