tudy types and the\naltmetric indicators, a weak but significant association was observed through\nthe chi-square and Cramers V. It is concluded that the positive association\nbetween altmetrics and study types in medicine could reflect the level of the\npyramid of scientific evidence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 00:05:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-20"}
