fusion and gravity-wave driven mixing may also\nplay roles. For late-G/K dwarfs, faster rotators show higher Li than slower\nrotators, and we discuss possible connections between angular momentum loss and\nLi depletion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 05:51:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2023 03:08:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2023 00:35:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-24"}
