ess the problem of accurately predicting structural and spin\nproperties of the solid-state defects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 09:14:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2023 13:41:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 14 Apr 2023 05:50:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-17"}
