RAC while maintaining an error under 3 % in the prediction of\nthe major and minor species, flame structure, and flame propagation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 15:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-20"}
