we find that $n$-th order\nFax\\'en operator are determined by the $n$-th order surface tractions, and the\nanalytical expression for the $0$-th, $1$-st and $2$-nd Fax\\'en operators for a\nsphere with Navier-slip boundary conditions is provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 15:46:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-20"}
